name: Matcha Strawberry Latte
description: Matcha is a Japanese green tea drink made from Camellia sinensis leaves, which have undergone a number of different botanical treatments. The leaves are dried and brewed into a special type of green tea that is then prepared by boiling the leaves, adding a special ingredient, Rooibos, and then steeping the resulting infusion in hot water for about an hour. The infusion is then poured into a glass and topped with a dollop of milk.
